quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  9,1,elaan baraat hai Allah aur is ke rasool ki taraf se unn mushriqeen ko jin se tum ne muahiday kiye thay
  9,2,"pas tum log malik mein chaar mahinay aur chal phir lau aur jaan rakho ke tum Allah ko aajiz karne walay nahi ho, aur yeh ke Allah munkareen haq ko ruswa karne wala hai"
  9,3,"ittila aam hai Allah aur is ke rasool ki taraf se hajj akbar ke din tamam logon ke liye ke Allah mushriqeen se buri alzmh hai aur uss ka rasool bhi ab agar tum log tauba kar lau to tumahray hi liye behtar hai aur jo mun phertey ho to khoob samajh lau ke tum Allah ko aajiz karne walay nahi ho aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inkaar karne walon ko sakht azaab ki khushkhabri suna do"
  9,4,"bajuz unn mushriqeen ke jin se tum ne maahd y kiye phir unhon ne apne ehad ko poora karne mein tumahray sath koi kami nahi ki aur nah tumahray khilaaf kisi ki madad ki, to aisay logon ke sath tum bhi muddat moahida taq wafa karo kyunkay Allah Muttaqiyun hi ko pasand karta hai"
  9,5,pas jab haraam mahinay guzar jayen to mushriqeen ko qatal karo jahan pao aur inhen pakro aur ghaayro aur har ghaat mein unn ki khabar lainay ke liye betho phir agar woh tauba kar len aur namaz qaim karen aur zkoh den to inhen chore do Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai
  9,6,aur agar mushriqeen mein se koi shakhs panah maang kar tumahray paas aana chahay ( taakay Allah ka kalaam sunay ) to ussay panah day do yahan taq ke woh Allah ka kalaam sun le phir ussay is kemaman (mehfooz jagah) taq pouncha do yeh is liye karna chahiye ke yeh log ilm nahi rakhtay
  9,7,"inn mushriqeen ke liye Allah aur is ke rasool ke nazdeek koi ehad aakhir kaisay ho sakta hai? bajuz unn logon ke jin se tum ne masjid haraam ke paas moahida kya tha, to jab taq woh tumahray sath seedhay rahen tum bhi un ke sath seedhay raho kyunkay Allah Muttaqiyun ko pasand karta hai"
  9,8,magar inn ke siwa dosray mushriqeen ke sath koi ehad kaisay ho sakta hai jabkay unn ka haal yeh hai ke tum par qaboo pa jayen to nah tumahray maamla mein kisi qaraabat ka lehaaz karen nah kisi moahida ki zimma daari ka woh apni zabanon se tum ko raazi karne ki koshish karte hain magar dil un ke inkaar karte hain aur un mein se aksar fasik hain
  9,9,unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ke badlay thori si qeemat qubool kar li phir Allah ke rastay mein sadday-rah (rokawat) ban kar kharray ho gay bohat buray kartoot thay jo yeh karte rahay
  9,10,kisi momin ke maamla mein nah yeh qaraabat ka lehaaz karte hain aur nah kisi ehad ki zimma daari ka aur zayad-ti hamesha unhi ki taraf se hui hai
  9,11,pas agar yeh tauba kar len aur namaz qaim karen aur zkoh den to tumahray dainee bhai hain aur jan-nay walon ke liye hum apne ehkaam wazeh kiye dete hain
  9,12,aur agar ehad karne ke baad yeh phir apni qasmon ko toar dalain aur tumahray deen par hamlay karne shuru kar den to kufar ke almbrdaron se jung karo kyunkay un ki qasmon ka aitbaar nahi shayad ke ( phir talwar hi ke zor se ) woh baz ayen ge
  9,13,kya tum nah lrho ge aisay logon se jo apne ehad torte rahay hain aur jinhon ne rasool ko malik se nikaal dainay ka qasad kya tha aur zayad-ti ki ibtida karne walay wohi thay? kya tum un se drtay ho? agar tum momin ho to Allah iss ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is se daro
  9,14,"un se lrho, Allah tumahray hathon se un ko saza dlwaye ga aur inhen zaleel o khawar kere ga aur un ke muqaabla mein tumhari madad kere ga aur bohat se mominoun ke dil thanday kere ga"
  9,15,"aur un ke qaloob ki jalan mita day ga, aur jisay chahay ga tauba ki tofeq bhi day ga Allah sab kuch jan-nay wala aur Dana hai"
  9,16,"kya tum logon ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke yuhin chore diye jao ge halaank abhi Allah ne yeh to dekha hi nahi ke tum mein se kon woh log hain jinhon ne ( is ki raah mein ) jaan fashani ki aur Allah aur rasool aur momnin ke siwa kisi ko jigaree dost nah banaya, jo kuch tum karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
  9,17,mushriqeen ka yeh kaam nahi hai ke woh Allah ki masjidoon ke Mujawer o khadim banindar-aa-n hala-n kehہ apne oopar woh khud kufar ki shahadat day rahay hain un ke to saaray aamaal zaya ho gay aur jahannum mein inhen hamesha rehna hai
  9,18,"Allah ki masjidoon ke abad car ( Mujawer o khadim ) to wohi log ho saktay hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir ko manen aur numa zay qaim karen, zkoh den aur Allah ke siwa kisi se nah dareen unhi se yeh tawaqqa hai ke seedhi raah chalein ge"
  9,19,kya tum logon ne hajion ko pani pilanay aur masjid haraam ki mjavri karne ko is shakhs ke kaam ke barabartehra liya hai jo imaan laya Allah par aur roz aakhir par aur jis ne jaanfishani ki Allah ki raah mein? Allah ke nazdeek to yeh dono barabar nahi hain aur Allah zaalmon ki rahnumai nahi karta
  9,20,Allah ke haan to unhi logon ka darja bara hai jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne is ki raah mein ghar baar chhorey aur jaan o maal se jehaad kya wohi kamyaab hain
  9,21,un ka rab inhen apni rehmat aur khushnodi aur aisijannaton ki basharat deta hai jahan un ke liye paidaar aish ke samaan hain
  9,22,un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yaqeenan Allah ke paas khidmaat ka sila dainay ko bohat kuch hai
  9,23,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apne bapon aur bhaiyon ko bhi apna Rafeeq nah banaao agar woh imaan par kufar ko tarjeeh den tum mein se jo un ko Rafeeq banayen ge wohi zalim hon ge"
  9,24,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke agar tumahray baap aur tumahray betay, aur tumahray bhai, aur tumhari biwiyan aur tumahray Aziz o Iqareb aur tumahray woh maal jo tum ne kama ye hain, aur tumahray woh kaarobar jin ke maand par jaane ka tum ko khauf hai aur tumahray woh ghar jo tum ko pasand hain, tum ko Allah aur is ke rasool aur is ki raah mein jehaad se Aziz tar hain to intzaar karo yahan taq ke Allah apna faisla tumahray samnay le aeye, aur Allah fasik logon ki rahnumai nahi kya karta"
  9,25,Allah is se pehlay bohat se mawaqay par tumhari madad kar chuka hai abhi Ghazwah Hunain ke roz ( uss ki dastgeeri ki shaan tum dekh chuke ho ) is roz tumhe apni kasrat tadaad ka Ghara tha magar woh tumahray kuch kaam nah aayi aur zameen apni wusat ke bawajood tum par tang ho gayi aur tum peeth phair kar bhaag niklay
  9,26,phir Allah ne apni sakinat (calm) apne rasool par aur momnin par nazil farmai aur woh lashkar utaarey jo tum ko nazar nah atay thay aur munkareen haq ko saza di ke yahi badla hai unn logon ke liye jo haq ka inkaar karen
  9,27,"phir ( tum yeh bhi dekh chuke ho ke ) is terhan saza dainay ke baad Allah jis ko chahta hai tauba ki tofeq bhi bakhash deta hai, Allah Dur guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  9,28,"ae imaan laane walo, mushriqeen napak hain lehaza is saal ke baad yeh masjid haraam ke qareeb nah phataknay payen aur agar tumhe tang dasti ka khauf hai to baeed nahi ke Allah chahay to tumhe a pannay fazl se ghanni kar day, Allah Aleem o hakeem hai"
  9,29,jung karo ahal kitaab mein se unn logon ke khilaaf jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan nahi laatay aur jo kuch Allah aur is ke rasool ne haraam qarar diya hai usay haraam nahi karte aur deen haq ko apna deen nahi banatay ( un se lrho ) yahan taq ke woh apne haath se jaziya den aur chhootey ban kar rahen
  9,30,"yahodi kehte hain ke Uzair Allah ka beta hai, aur isaai kehte hain ke maseeh Allah ka beta hai yeh be haqeeqat baatein hain jo woh apni zabanon se nikaltay hain unn logon ki dekha dekhi jo un se pehlay kufar mein mubtala hue thay khuda ki maar inn par, yeh kahan se dhoka khaar hai hain"
  9,31,"unhon ne apne ulama aur darwaishoo-n ko Allah ke siwa apna rab bana liya hai aur isi terhan maseeh Ibn maryam ko bhi halaank un ko aik mabood ke siwa kisi ki bandagi karne ka hukum nahi diya gaya tha, woh jis ke siwa koi mustahiq ibadat nahi, pak hai woh un mushrikana baton se jo yeh log karte hain"
  9,32,yeh log chahtay hain ke Allah ki roshni ko apni phoonko se bujha den magar Allah apni roshni ko mukammal kiye baghair maan-ne wala nahi hai khuwa kafiroon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
  9,33,woh Allah hi hai jis ne apne rasool ko hadaayat aur deen haq ke sath bheja hai taakay usay poori jins deen par ghalib kar day khuwa mushrikon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
  9,34,"ae imaan laane walo, inn ahal kitaab ke aksar ulama aur darwaishoo-n ka haal yeh hai ke woh logon ke maal baatil tareeqon se khatay hain aur inhen Allah ki raah se roktay hain dard naak saza ki khush khaberi do un ko jo sonay aur chandi jama kar ke rakhtay hain aur inhen khuda ki raah mein kharch nahi karte"
  9,35,"aik din aeye ga ke isi sonay chandi par jahannum ki aag dehkai jaye gi aur phir isi se un logon ki pishanyon aur pehluo aur pithon ko dagha jaye ga yeh hai woh khazana jo tum ne apne liye jama kya tha, lau ab apni smiti hui doulat ka maza chako"
  9,36,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke mahino ki tadaad jab se Allah ne aasman o zameen ko peda kya hai Allah ke noshte mein baara hi hai, aur un mein se chaar mahinay haraam hain yahi theek zabita hai lehaza un chaar mahino mein apne oopar zulm nah karo aur mushrikon se sab mil kar lrho jis terhan woh sab mil kar tum se lartay hain aur jaan rakho ke Allah Muttaqiyun hi ke sath hai"
  9,37,"nasee to kufar mein aik mazeed kafirana harkat hai jis se yeh kafir log gumraahi mein mubtala kiye jatay hain kisi saal aik mahinay ko halal kar letay hain aur kisi saal uss ko haraam kar dete hain, taakay Allah ke haraam kiye hue mahino ki tadaad poori bhi kar den aur Allah ka haraam kya howa halal bhi kar len un ke buray aamaal un ke liye khushnuma bana diye gay hain aur Allah munkareen haq ko hadaayat nahi diya karta"
  9,38,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumhe kya ho gaya ke jab tum se Allah ki raah mein niklny ke liye kaha gaya to tum zameen se chimat kar reh gay? kya tum ne akhirat ke muqaabla mein duniya ki zindagi ko pasand kar liya? aisa hai to tumhe maloom ho ke dunewi zindagi ka yeh sab srosaman akhirat mein bohat thora niklay ga"
  9,39,"tum nah utho ge to khuda tumhe dard naak saza day ga, aur tumhari jagah kisi aur giroh ko uthaye ga, aur tum khuda ka kuch bhi nah bigaar sakuu ge, woh har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
  9,40,"tum ne agar NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki madad nah ki to kuch parwa nahi, Allah uss ki madad is waqt kar chuka hai jab kafiroon ne usay nikaal diya tha, jab woh sirf do mein ka dosra tha, jab woh dono ghaar mein thay, jab woh apni saathi se keh raha tha ke"" gham nah kar, Allah hamaray sath hai"" uss waqt Allah ne is par apni taraf se sukoon qalb nazil kya aur is ki madad aisay lashkaron se ki jo tum ko nazar nah atay thay aur kafiroon ka bol neecha kar diya aur Allah ka bol to ouncha hi hai, Allah zabardast aur Dana o Beena hai"
  9,41,"niklo, khuwa halkay ho ya boujhal, aur jehaad karo Allah ki raah mein apne malon aur apni jaanun ke sath, yeh tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum jano"
  9,42,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, agar faida sehal ul husool hota aur safar halka hota to woh zaroor tumahray peechay chalne par amaada ho jatay, magar un par to yeh rasta bohat kathin ho gaya ab woh khuda ki qasam kha kha kar kahin ge ke agar hum chal satke to yaqeenan tumahray sath chaltay woh apne aap ko halakat mein daal rahay hain Allah khoob jaanta hai ke woh jhutay hain"
  9,43,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, Allah tumhe maaf kere, tum ne kyun inhen rukhsat day di? ( tumhe chahiye tha ke khud rukhsat nah dete ) taakay tum par khil jata ke kon log sachey hain aur jhoton ko bhi tum jaan letay"
  9,44,jo log Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay hain woh to kabhi tum se yeh darkhwast nah karen ge ke inhen apni jaan o maal ke sath jehaad karne se maaf rakha jaye Allah Muttaqiyun ko khoob jaanta hai
  9,45,"aisi darkhwasten to sirf wohi log karte hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan nahi rakhtay, jin ke dilon mein shak hai aur woh apne shak hi mein متردد ho rahay hain"
  9,46,"agar waqai un ka iradah niklny ka hota to woh is ke liye kuch tayari karte lekin Allah ko un ka uthna pasand hinah tha, is liye is ne inhen sust kar diya aur keh diya ke baith raho bethnay walon ke sath"
  9,47,"agar woh tumahray sath nikaltay to tumahray andar kharabi ke siwa kisi cheez ka izafah nah karte woh tumahray darmain fitnah pardazi ke liye daud dhoop karte, aur tumahray giroh ka haal yeh hai ke abhi uss mein bohat se aisay log mojood hain jo unn ki baatein kaan laga kar suntay hain, Allah inn zaalmon ko khoob jaanta hai"
  9,48,is se pehlay bhi inn logon ne fitnah angazi ki koshishen ki hain aur tumhe nakaam karne ke liye yeh har terhan ki tdbiron ka ulat phair kar chuke hain yahan taq ke un ki marzi ke khilaaf haq aa gaya aur Allah ka kaam ho kar raha
  9,49,"un mein se koi hai jo kehta hai ke"" mujhe rukhsat day degiye aur mujh ko ftne mein nah dalie"" sun rakho! ftne hi mein to yeh log parre hue hain aur jahannum ne un kafiroon ko ghair rakha hai"
  9,50,tumhara bhala hota hai to inhen ranj hota hai aur tum par koi museebat aati hai to yeh mun phair kar khush khush palatne hain aur kehte jatay hain ke acha howa hum ne pehlay hi apna maamla theek kar liya tha
  9,51,"un se kaho"" hamein hargiz koi ( buraiee ya bhalai ) nahi pahunchti magar woh jo Allah ne hamaray liye likh di hai Allah hi hamara Mooli hai, aur ahal imaan ko isi par bharosa karna chahiye """
  9,52,"un se kaho,"" tum hamaray maamla mein jis cheez ke muntazir ho woh is ke siwa aur kya hai ke do bhulaiyon mein se aik bhalai hai aur hum tumahray maamla mein jis cheez ke muntazir hain woh yeh hai ke Allah khud tum ko saza deta hai ya hamaray hathon dlwata hai? acha to ab tum bhi intzaar karo aur hum bhi tumahray sath muntazir hain """
  9,53,"un se kaho"" tum apne maal khuwa raazi khusi kharch karo ya ba-karahat, bahar haal woh qubool nah kiye jayen ge kyunkay tum fasik log ho """
  9,54,"un ke diye hue maal qubool nah honay ki koi wajah is ke siwa nahi hai ke unhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool se kufar kya hai, namaz ke liye atay hain to kasmsakatay hue atay hain aur raah khuda mein kharch karte hain to baadal nakhwast_h kharch karte hain"
  9,55,"inn ke maal o doulat aur un ki kasrat aulaad ko dekh kar dhoka nah khao, Allah to yeh chahta hai ke aِnhi cheezon ke zareya se un ko duniya ki zindagi mein bhi mbtlaye azaab kere aur yeh jaan bhi den to inkaar haq hi ki haalat mein den"
  9,56,"woh khuda ki qasam kha kha kar kehte hain ke hum tumhi mein se hain, halaank woh hargiz tum mein se nahi hain asal mein to woh aisay log hain jo tum se khauf zada hain"
  9,57,"agar woh koi jaye panah paleen ya koi khoh ya ghis bethnay ki jagah, to bhaag kar uss mein ja chhpin"
  9,58,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un mein se baaz log sadqat ki taqseem mein tum par aitrazaat karte hain agar is maal mein se inhen kuch day diya jaye to khoo sh ho jayen, aur nah diya jaye to bighrnay lagtay hain"
  9,59,"kya acha hota ke Allah aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne jo kuch bhi inhen diya tha is par woh raazi rehtay aur kehte ke"" Allah hamaray liye kaafi hai, woh apne fazl se hamein bohat kuch day ga aur is ka rasool bhi hum par inayat farmaiye ga, hum Allah hi ki taraf nazar jamaye hue hain """
  9,60,"yeh sadqat to darasal faqeero aur miskeeno ke liye hain aur unn logon ke liye jo sadqat ke kaam par mamoor hon, aur unn ke liye jin ki taleef qalb matloob ho neez yeh gardnon ke chhuranay aur qarz daaron ki madad karne mein aur raah khuda mein aur musafir nawazi mein istemaal karne ke liye hain aik fareeza hai Allah ki taraf se aur Allah sab kuch jan-nay wala aur Dana o Beena hai"
  9,61,"un mein se kuch log hain jo apni baton se nabi ko dukh dete hain aur kehte hain ke yeh shakhs kaanon ka kacha hai kaho,"" woh tumhari bhalai ke liye aisa hai, Allah par imaan rakhta hai aur ahal imaan par aetmaad karta hai aur sara sar rehmat hai un logon ke liye jo tum mein se imandaar hain aur jo log Allah ke rasool ko dukh dete hain un ke liye dard naak saza hai """
  9,62,"yeh log tumahray samnay kasmain khatay hain taakay tumhe raazi karen, halaank agar yeh momin hain to Allah aur rasool is ke ziyada haq daar hain ke yeh un ko raazi karne ki fikar karen"
  9,63,kya inhen maloom nahi hai ke jo Allah aur is ke rasool ka muqaabla karta hai is ke liye dozakh ki aag hai jis mein woh hamesha rahay ga yeh bohat barri ruswai hai
  9,64,"yeh munafiq dar rahay hain ke kahin musalmanoon par koi aisi sourat nazil nah ho jaye jo un ke dilon ke bhaid khol kar rakh day ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho,"" aur mazaq urrao, Allah uss cheez ko khol dainay wala hai jis ke khil jaane se tum drtay ho """
  9,65,"agar un se pucho ke tum kya baatein kar rahay thay, to jhat keh den ge ke hum to hansi mazaq aur dil lagi kar rahay thay un se kaho,"" kya tumhari hansi dil lagi Allah aur uss ki ayaat aur is ke rasool hi ke sath thi ?"
  9,66,"ab uzraat nahtrasho tum ne imaan laane ke baad kufar kya hai, agar hum ne tum mein se aik giroh ko maaf kar bhi diya to dosray giroh ko to hum zaroor saza den ge kyunkay woh mujrim hai """
  9,67,munafiq mard aur munafiq aurtain sab aik dosray ke hum rang hain buraiee ka hukum dete hain aur bhalai se mana karte hain aur apne haath kher se rokay rakhtay hain yeh Allah ko bhool gay to Allah ne bhi inhen bhala diya yaqeenan yeh munafiq hi fasik hain
  9,68,"un munafiq mardon aur aurton aur kafiroon ke liye Allah ne aatish dozakh ka wada kya hai jis mein woh hamesha rahen ge, wohi un ke liye mozoon hai un par Allah ki phatkaar hai aur un ke liye qaim rehnaywala azaab hai"
  9,69,"tum logon ke rang dhang wohi hain jo tumahray paish roon ke thay woh tum se ziyada zor aawar aur tum se barh kar maal aur aulaad walay thay phir unhon ne duniya mein apne hissa ke mazay lout liye aur tum ne bhi apne hissay ke mazay isi terhan lautay jaisay unhon ne lautay thay, aur waisi hi bhson mein tum bhi parre jaisi bhson mein woh parre thay, so un ka injaam yeh howa ke duniya aur akhirat mein un ka sab kya dhara zaya ho gaya aur wohi khasaray mein hain"
  9,70,"kya inn logon ko apne paish roon ki tareekh nahi pohanchi? Nooh ki qoum, Aad , smod, ibrahim ki qoum, Mudin ke log aur woh bastiyan jinhein ulat diya gaya unn ke rasool un ke paas khuli khuli nishanain le kar aeye, phir yeh Allah ka kaam nah tha ke un par zulm karta magar woh aap hi apne oopar zulm karne walay thay"
  9,71,"momin mard aur momin aurtain, yeh sab aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain, bhalai ka hukum dete aur buraiee se roktay hain, namaz qaim karte hain, zkoh dete hain aur Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte hain yeh woh log hain jin par Allah ki rehmat nazil ho kar rahay gi, yaqeenan Allah sab par ghalib aur hakeem o Dana hai"
  9,72,"un momin mardon aur aurton se Allah ka wada hai ke inhen aisay baagh day ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge un sada bahhar baghoon mein un ke liye pakeeza qiyam gahin hon gi, aur sab se barh kar yeh ke Allah ki khushnodi inhen haasil hogi yahi barri kamyabi hai"
  9,73,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kufar aur munafiqeen dono ka poori qowat se muqaabla karo aur un ke sath sakhti se paish aao aakhir-kaar un ka thikana jahannum hai aur woh bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
  9,74,"yeh log khuda ki qasam kha kha kar kehte hain ke hum ne woh baat nahi kahi, halaank unhon ne zaroor woh kafirana baat kahi hai woh islam laane ke baad kufar ke murtakib hue aur unhon ne woh kuch karne ka iradah kya jisay kar nah sakay yeh un ka sara gussa isi baat par hai na ke Allah aur is ke rasool ne apne fazl se un ko ghanni kar diya hai! ab agar yeh apni is rawish se baz aa jayen to unhi ke liye behtar hai aur agar yeh baz nah aeye to Allah un ko nihayat dard naak saza day ga, duniya mein bhi aur akhirat mein bhi, aur zameen mein koi nahi jo inn ka himayati aur madadgaar ho"
  9,75,un mein se baaz aisay bhi hain jinhon ne Allah se ehad kya tha ke agar is ne apne fazl se hum ko nawaza to hum khairaat karen ge aur Saleh ban kar rahen ge
  9,76,magar jab Allah ne apne fazl se un ko doulat mand kar diya to woh bukhal par utar aeye aur apne ehad se aisay phiray ke inhen is ki parwa taq nahi hai
  9,77,"nateeja yeh nikla ke un ki iss bad ehdi ki wajah se jo unhon ne Allah ke sath ki, aur is jhoot ki wajah se jo woh boltay rahay, Allah ne un ke dilon mein nifaq bitha diya jo is ke huzoor un ki paishi ke din taq un ka peecha nah chhorey ga"
  9,78,kya yeh log jantay nahi hain ke Allah ko un ke makhfi raaz aur un ki posheeda sargoshian taq maloom hain aur woh tamam ghaib ki baton se poori terhan bakhabar hai ?
  9,79,( woh khoob jaanta hai unn kanjoos doulat mandoon ko ) jo brza o raghbat dainay walay ahal imaan ki maali qurbanion par baatein chant-tayhain aur un logon ka mazaq uratay hain jin ke paas ( raah khuda mein dainay ke liye ) uss ke siwa kuch nahi hai jo woh apne oopar mushaqqat bardasht kar ke dete hain Allah inn mazaq urane walon ka mazaq urata hai aur un ke liye dard naak saza hai
  9,80,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum khuwa aisay logon ke liye maffi ki darkhwast karo ya nah karo, agar tum sattar martaba bhi inhen maaf kardainay ki darkhwast karo ge to Allah inhen hargiz maaf nah kere ga is liye ke unhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool ke sath kufar kya hai, aur Allah fasik logon ko raah nijaat nahi dekhata"
  9,81,"jin logon ko peechay reh jaane ki ijazat day di gayi thi woh Allah ke rasool ka sath nah dainay aur ghar baithy rehne par khush hue aur inhen gawara nah howa ke Allah ki raah mein jaan o maal se jehaad karen unhon ne logon se kaha ke"" is sakht garmi mein nah niklo"" un se kaho ke jahannum ki aag is se ziyada garam hai, kash inhen is ka shaoor hota"
  9,82,"ab chahiye ke yeh log hansna kam karen aur royain ziyada, is liye ke jo badi yeh kamate rahay hain is ki jaza aisi hi hai ( ke inhen is par rona chahiye )"
  9,83,"agar Allah un ke darmain tumhe wapas le jaye aur aindah un mein se koi giroh jehaad ke liye niklny ki tum se ijazat mangay to saaf keh dena ke,"" ab tum mere sath hargiz nahi chal satke aur nah meri mayt mein kisi dushman se lar satke ho, tum ne pehlay baith rehnay ko pasand kya tha to ab ghar bethnay walon hi ke sath baithy raho """
  9,84,aur aindah un mein se jo koi marey is ki namaz e janaza bhi tum hargiz nah parhna aur nah kabhi is ki qabar par kharray hona kyunkay unhon ne Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath kufar kya hai aur woh marey hain is haal mein ke woh fasik thay
  9,85,un ki maldari aur un ki kasrat aulaad tum ko dhokay mein nah daaley Allah ne to iradah kar liya hai ke iss maal o aulaad ke zareya se un ko isi duniya mein saza day aur un ki jaanen is haal mein nikleen ke woh kafir hon
  9,86,jab kabhi koi surah is mazmoon ki nazil hui ke Allah ko manu aur is ke rasool ke sath jehaad karo to tum ne dekha ke jo log un mein se sahib mqdrt thay wohi tum se darkhwast karne lagey ke inhen jehaad ki shirkat se maaf rakha jaye aur unhon ne kaha ke hamein chore degiye ke hum bethnay walon ke sath rahen
  9,87,"un logon ne ghar bethnay valyon mein shaamil hona pasand kya aur un ke dilon par thp_h laga diya gaya, is liye un ki samajh mein ab kuch nahi aata"
  9,88,bakhilaf is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne aur un logon ne jo Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke sath imaan laaye thay a panni jaan o maal se jehaad kya aur ab saari bhalaiyan unhi ke liye hain aur wohi Falah panay walay hain
  9,89,"Allah ne un ke liye aisay baagh tayyar rakhay hain jin ke neechay nhrin bah rahi hain, un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yeh hai azeem al shan kamyabi"
  9,90,badwi arbo mein se bhi bohat se log aeye jinhon ne izr kiye taakay inhen bhi peechay reh jaane ki ijazat di jaye iss terhan baith rahay woh log jinhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool se imaan ka jhoota ehad kya tha unbadwiyoonmein se jin logon ne kufar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kya hai anqareeb woh dard naak saza se dochar hon ge
  9,91,"zaeef aur bemaar log aur woh log jo shirkat jehaad ke liye raah nahi paate, agar peechay reh jayen to koi harj nahi jabkay woh khuloos dil ke sath Allah aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke wafadar hon aisay mohsineenpar aitraaz ki koi gunjaish nahi hai aur Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  9,92,"isi terhan unn logon par bhi koi aitraaz ka mauqa nahi hai jinhon ne khud aa kar tum se darkhwast ki thi ke hamaray liye swaryan baham pohanchai jayen, aur jab tum ne kaha ke mein tumahray liye swaryon ka intizam nahi karsaktha to woh majaburan wapas gay aur haal yeh tha ke un ki aankhon se ansoo jari thay aur inhen is baat ka bara ranj tha ke woh apne kharch par shareek jehaad honay ki mqdrt nahi rakhtay"
  9,93,"Albata aitraaz un logon par hai jo maldaar hain aur phir bhi tum se darkhwasten karte hain ke inhen shirkat jehaad se maaf rakha jaye unhon ne ghar bethnay valyon mein shaamil hona pasand kya aur Allah ne un ke dilon par thp_h laga diya, is liye ab yeh kuch nahi jantay ( ke Allah ke haan un ki rawish ka kya nateeja niklny wala hai )"
  9,94,"tum jab palat kar un ke paas pohncho ge to yeh terhan terhan ke azraat paish karen ge magar tum saaf keh dena ke"" bahanay nah karo, hum tumhari kisi baat ka aitbaar nah karen ge Allah ne hum ko tumahray halaat bta diye hain ab Allah aur is ka rasool tumahray tarz amal ko dekhe ga phir tum is ki taraf palta-ay jao ge jo khulay aur chupay sab ka jan-nay wala hai aur woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya kuch karte rahay ho """
  9,95,"tumhari wapsi par yeh tumahray samnay kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se sirf nazar karo to be shak tum un se sirf nazar hi kar lau, kyunkay yeh gandagi hain aur un ka asli maqam jahannum hai jo un ki kamaai ke badlay mein inhen naseeb hogi"
  9,96,yeh tumahray samnay kasmain khayen ge ke taakay tum un se raazi ho jao halaank agar tum un se raazi ho bhi gay to Allah hargiz aisay fasik logon se raazi nah hoga
  9,97,yeh badwi arab kufar o nifaq mein ziyada sakht hain aur un ke maamla mein is amar ke imkanaat ziyada hain ke is deen ke hudood se na waaqif rahen jo Allah ne apne rasool par nazil kya hai Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur hakeem o Dana hai
  9,98,unbadwiyonmein aisay aisay log mojood hain jo raah khuda mein kuch kharch karte hain to usay apne oopar zabardasti ki chti samajte hain aur tumahray haq mein zamana ki gardishon ka intzaar kar rahay hain ( ke tum kisi chakkar mein phanso tuwoh apni gardan se is nizaam ki itaat ka qladah utaar phankein jis mein tum ne inhen kis diya hai ) halaank badi ka chakkar khud unhi par musallat hai aur Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai
  9,99,"aur unhi dabwiyonmein kuch log aisay bhi hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay hain aur jo kuch kharch karte hain ussay Allah ke taqarab ka aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki taraf se rehmat ki duayen lainay ka zareya banatay hain haan! woh zaroor un ke liye taqarab ka zareya hai aur Allah zaroor un ko apni rehmat mein daakhil karega, yaqeenan Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  9,100,"woh mohajir o Ansar jinhon ne sab se pehlay dawat imaan par labaik kehnay mein Sabqat ki, neez woh jo baad meinrasbaazی ke sath peechay aeye, Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se raazi hue, Allah ne un ke liye aisay baagh muhayya kar rakhay hain jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi aur woh un mein hamesha rahen ge, yahi azeem al shan kamyabi hai"
  9,101,"tumahray gird o paish jo badwi rehtay hain un mein bohat se munafiq hain aur isi terhan khud madinah ke bashindon mein bhi munafiq mojood hain jo nifaq mein taaq ho gay hain tum inhen nahi jantay, hum un ko jantay hain qareeb hai woh waqt jab hum un ko dohri saza den ge, phir woh ziyada barri saza ke liye wapas laaye jayen ge"
  9,102,"kuch aur log hain jinhon ne apneKasoroo-n ka aitraaf kar liya hai un ka amal makhloot hai, kuch naik hai aur kuch bad, baeed nahi ke Allah un par phir meharban ho jaye kyunkay woh dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  9,103,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum un ke amwal mein se sadqa le kar inhen pak karo aur ( neki ki raah mein ) inhen barhao, aur un ke haq mein duaye rehmat karo kyunkay tumhari dua un ke liye wajah taskeen hogi, Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  9,104,"kya inn logon ko maloom nahi hai ke woh Allah hi hai jo apne bundon ki tauba qubool karta hai aur un ki khairaat ko qabuliat ataa farmata hai, aur yeh ke Allah bohat maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai ?"
  9,105,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se kehdo ke tum amal karo, Allah aur is ka rasool aur momnin sab dekhen ge ke tumhara tarz amal ab kya rehta hai phir tum uss ki taraf palta-ayjao ge jo khulay aur chupay sab ko jaanta hai aur woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya karte rahay ho"
  9,106,"kuch Dosar y log hain jin ka maamla abhi khuda ke hukum partehra howa hai, chahay inhen saza day aur chahay unn par az sir no meharban ho jaye Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur hakeem o Dana hai"
  9,107,"kuch aur log hain jinhon ne aik masjid banai iss gharz ke liye ke ( dawat haq ko ) nuqsaan p_hnchayin, aur ( khuda ki bandagi karne ke bajaye ) kufar karen, aur ahal imaan mein phoot dalain, aur ( is bzahir ibadat gaah ko ) uss shakhs ke liye kameen gaah banayen jo is se pehlay khuda aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke khilaaf Bar sir pekaar ho chuka hai woh zaroor kasmain kha kha kar kahin ge ke hamara iradah to bhalai ke siwa kisi doosri cheez ka nah tha magar Allah gawah hai ke woh qatee jhutay hain"
  9,108,"tum hargiz is imarat mein kharray nah hona jo masjid awwal roz se taqwa par qaim ki gayi thi wohi is ke liye ziyada mozoon hai ke tum is mein ( Ibad t- ke liye ) kharray ho, is mein aisay log hain jo pak rehna pasand karte hain aur Allah ko pakizgee ikhtiyar karne walay hi pasand hain"
  9,109,phir tumhara kya khayaal hai ke behtar ensaan woh hai jis ne apni imarat ki bunyaad khuda ke khauf aur is ki Raza ki talab par rakhi ho ya woh jis ne apni imarat aik waadi ki khokhli be Sabaat kagar par uthai aur woh usay le kar seedhi jahannum ki aag mein ja giri? aisay zalim logon ko Allah kabhi seedhi raah nahi dekhata
  9,110,"yeh imarat jo unhon ne banai hai, hamesha un ke dilon mein be yakeeni ki jarr bani rahay gi ( jis ke niklny ki ab koi soorat nahi ) bajuz is ke ke un ke dil hi Parah Parah ho jayen Allah nihayat bakhabar aur hakeem o Dana hai"
  9,111,"haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ne mominoun se un ke nafs aur un ke maal jannat ke badlay khareed liye hain woh Allah ki raah mein lartay aur maartay aur martay hain un se ( jannat ka wada ) Allah ke zimmay aik pukhta wada hai Touraat aur injeel aur quran mein aur kon hai jo Allah se barh kar apne ehad ka poora karne wala ho? pas khusihyan maanao apne is saudey par jo tum ne khuda se chuka liya hai, yahi sab se barri kamyabi hai"
  9,112,"Allah ki taraf baar baar palatnay walay, uss ke bandagi baja laane walay, uss ki tareef ke gun ganay walay, uss ki khatir zameen mein gardish karne walay, uss ke agay ruku aur sjday karne walay, neki ka hukum dainay walay, badi se roknay walay, aur Allah ke hudood ki hifazat karne walay, ( is shaan ke hotay hain woh momin jo Allah se khareed o farokht ka yeh maamla tey karte hain ) aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam un mominoun ko khush khaberi day do"
  9,113,"NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko aur unn logon ko jo imaan laaye hain, zaiba nahi hai ke mushrikon ke liye mughfirat ki dua karen, chahay woh un ke rishta daar hi kyun nah hon, jabkay un par yeh baat khil chuki hai ke woh jahannum ke mustahiq hain"
  9,114,"ibrahim ne apne baap ke liye jo duaye mughfirat ki thi woh to uss waday ki wajah se thi jo is ne apne baap se kya tha, magar jab is par yeh baat khil gayi ke is ka baap khuda ka dushman hai to woh is se bezaar ho gaya, haq yeh hai ke ibrahim bara raqeeq ul qalb o Khuda tars aur Burdbar aadmi tha"
  9,115,Allah ka yeh tareeqa nahi hai ke logon ko hadaayat dainay ke baad phir gumraahi mein mubtala kere jab taq ke inhen saaf saaf bta nah day ke inhen kin cheezon se bachna chahiye dar haqeeqat Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
  9,116,"aur yeh bhi waqea hai ke Allah hi ke qabza mein aasman o zameen ki saltanat hai, isi ke ikhtiyar mein zindagi o mout hai, aur tumhara koi haami o madadgaar aesa hai jo tumhe is se bacha sakay"
  9,117,"Allah ne maaf kar diya NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ko aur un muhajreen o Ansar ko jinhon ne barri tangi ke waqt mein NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka sath diya agar chay un mein se kuch logon ke dil kajji ki taraf mael ho chuke thay ( magar jab unhon ne is kajji ka itebaa nah kya balkay NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ka sath hi diya to ) Allah ne inhen maaf kar diya, be shak uss ka maamla inn logon ke sath shafqat o meharbani ka hai"
  9,118,"aur unn tenu ko bhi is ne maaf kya jin ke maamla ko multawi kar diya gaya tha jab zameen apni saari wusat ke bawajood un par tang ho gayi aur un ki apni jaanen bhi un par baar honay lagen aur unhon ne jaan liya ke Allah se bachney ke liye koi jaye panah khud Allah hi ke daman rehmat ke siwa nahi hai, to Allah apni meharbani se un ki taraf palta taakay woh is ki taraf palat ayen, yaqeenan woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  9,119,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro aur sachey logon ka sath do"
  9,120,"madeeney ke bashindon aur gird o nawah ke badwiyonko yeh hargiz zaiba nah tha ke Allah ke rasool ko chore kar ghar baith rehtay aur is ki taraf se be parwa ho kar apne apne nafs ki fikar mein lag jatay is liye ke aisa kabhi nah hoga ke Allah ki raah mein bhook pyaas aur jismani mushaqqat ki koi takleef woh jhelen, aur munkareen haq ko jo raah nagawaar hai uss par koi qadam woh utthayen, aur kisi dushman se ( adawat haq ka ) ka koi intiqam woh len aur is ke badlay un ke haq mein aik amal Saleh nah likha jaye yaqeenan Allah ke haan mohsinon ka haq alkhdmt mara nahi jata hai"
  9,121,isi terhan yeh bhi kabhi nah hoga ke ( raah khuda mein ) thora ya bohat koi kharch woh utthayen aur ( sae jehaad mein ) koi waadi woh paar karen aur un ke haq mein usay likh nah liya jaye taakay Allah un ke is achay karname ka sila inhen ataa kere
  9,122,"aur yeh kuch zurori nah tha ke ahal imaan saaray ke saaray hi nikal kharray hotay, magar aisa kyun nah howa ke un ki abadi ke har hissa mein se kuch log nikal kar atay aur deen ki samajh peda karte aur wapas ja kar apne ilaqay ke bashindon ko khabardaar karte taakay woh ( ghair musalmana rawish se ) parhaiz karte"
  9,123,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jung karo unn munkareen haq se jo tum se qareeb hain aur chahiye ke woh tumahray andar sakhti payen, aur jaan lau ke Allah Muttaqiyun ke sath hai"
  9,124,"jab koi nai sourat nazil hoti hai to un mein se baaz log ( mazaq ke tor par musalmanoon se ) puchhte hain ke"" kaho, tum mein se kis ke imaan mein is se izafah howa ?"" ( is ka jawab yeh hai ke ) jo log imaan laaye hain un ke imaan mein to fi al waqea ( har nazil honay wali sourat ne ) izafah hi kya hai aur woh is se dilshaad hain"
  9,125,Albata jin logon ke dilon ko ( nifaq ka ) rog laga howa tha unn ki sabiq najasat par ( har nai sourat ne ) aik aur najasat ka izafah kar diya aur woh martay dam taq kufar hi mein mubtala rahay
  9,126,kya yeh log dekhte nahi ke har saal aik do martaba yeh azmaish mein daaley jatay hain? magar iss par bhi nah tauba karte hain nah koi sabaq letay hain
  9,127,"jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai to yeh log aankhon hi aankhon mein aik dosray se baatein karte hain ke kahin koi tum ko dekh to nahi raha hai, phir chupkay se nikal bhagtay hain Allah ne un ke dil phair diye hain kyunkay yeh nasamajh log hain"
  9,128,"dekho! tum logon ke paas aik rasool aaya hai jo khud tum hi mein se hai, tumhara nuqsaan mein parna is par shaq hai, tumhari Falah ka woh harees hai, imaan laane walon ke liye woh shafeeq aur Raheem hai"
  9,129,"ab agar yeh log tum se mun phertey hain to ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kehdo ke"" mere liye Allah bas karta hai, koi mabood nahi magar woh, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur woh maalik hai arsh azeem ka """
